import React from "react";
import Grid from "@material-ui/core/Grid";
import FooterMakeStyle from "./FooterMakeStyle";
import Typography from "@material-ui/core/Typography";

export default function Footer() {
  const classes = FooterMakeStyle();

  return (
    <footer style={{ margin: 0, padding: 0 }}>
      <Grid>
        <Grid
          container
          direction="row"
          className={classes.footerContainer}
          justify="space-evenly"
          alignItems="center"
          //   spacing={6}
        >
          <Grid item>
            <Grid container direction="column" spacing={4}>
              <Grid item>
                <Typography variant="h5">Our solutions</Typography>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item>
                <Typography variant="body1">Design & creatives</Typography>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item>
                <Typography variant="body1">Telecommunication</Typography>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item>
                <Typography variant="body1">Restaurant</Typography>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item>
                <Typography variant="body1">Programing</Typography>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item>
                <Typography variant="body1">Architecture</Typography>
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>

          <Grid item>
            <Grid container direction="column" spacing={4}>
              <Grid item>
                <Typography variant="h5">Our solutions</Typography>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item>
                <Typography variant="body1">Design & creatives</Typography>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item>
                <Typography variant="body1">Telecommunication</Typography>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item>
                <Typography variant="body1">Restaurant</Typography>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item>

              </Grid>
              <Grid item>
                <Typography variant="body1">Architecture</Typography>
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>

          <Grid item>
            <Grid container direction="column" spacing={4}>
              <Grid item>
                <Typography variant="h5">Our solutions</Typography>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item>
                <Typography variant="body1">Design & creatives</Typography>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item>
                <Typography variant="body1">Telecommunication</Typography>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item>
                <Typography variant="body1">Restaurant</Typography>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item>
                <Typography variant="body1">Programing</Typography>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item>
                <Typography variant="body1">Architecture</Typography>
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </footer>
  );
}
